Basic master/slaves system based on mpi4py online tutorial:
http://mpi4py.scipy.org/docs/usrman/tutorial.html

1) to run, just issue "make"
2) mpiexec invoked with single processor to run the master program
3) master spawn a number of processors and divides the calculation
   between them
4) clients reduce their calcs, then master its own
5) ...
6) PROFIT!
